entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have put the poor engineered creatures out of their misery. All that remains is to destroy the research data.
entries.journal_entry_description: Head down to the Zoo and clean house.
entries.journal_entry_title: Coronet Murmurs: Clear Out the Zoo
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 4 of the engineered tusk-cats while they are sedated.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 6 of the engineered spiders while they are sedated.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 5 of the engineered mites while they are sedated.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 5 of the engineered klikniks while they are sedated.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 5 of the engineered durnis while they are sedated.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: This horrific holding pen houses creatures that are suffering as much as they could cause others to suffer. Kill them and put them out of their misery.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Kill the engineered acklay in its lair.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Kill the boar wolf in its lair.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Kill the creatures that were too dangerous to keep with the others.
entries.task10_comm_message_text: Very good work! All you need to do is destroy their main computer. This operation needs to be eliminated now.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: You received a message from Lt. Joth: Very good work! All you need to do is destroy their main computer. This operation needs to be eliminated now.
